@startuml
title Action Manager 리팩토링 구조 (Astra 기반 멀티 브로커 대응)

package "Astra Engine" {
    component "Broker Manager" as BrokerManager
    component "Broker Adapter\n(MQTT/ZMQ/기타)" as BrokerAdapter
}

package "Astra Core" {
    component "Action Dispatcher" as ActionDispatcher
    component "Action Manager" as ActionManager
    component "Action Base" as ActionBase
}

package "Actions" {
    component "Custom Action\n(예: NcActionBarcodeReader)" as CustomAction
    component "Custom Action2\n(예: NcActionMove)" as CustomAction2
}

BrokerManager --> BrokerAdapter : 멀티 브로커 관리
BrokerAdapter --> ActionDispatcher : 메시지 전달 (REQ/REP, PUB/SUB)

ActionDispatcher --> ActionManager : Action 실행 요청
ActionManager --> ActionBase : Action 공통 로직
ActionBase <|-- CustomAction
ActionBase <|-- CustomAction2

ActionManager --> ActionDispatcher : Action 결과 전달
ActionDispatcher --> BrokerAdapter : 브로커 응답 처리
@enduml